Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:07.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完了 怎麼回事啊這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:10.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我們一起做也做不完的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:15.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們學校的作業量和傳聞中一樣變態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:20.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明想趕快做完開始準備考試的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:26.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是不是也該和小繪一樣去補習班了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:28.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥你打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:31.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概冬天開始去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:34.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我家沒錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:37.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:42.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我做完作業就去和老師告白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:47.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:50.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎 同時去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:54.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,結果我還是趁勢而上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:14.50,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}一番大切なものを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:16.97,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}一番大切にしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:21.56,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}そんな単純なことが今は一番出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:24.43,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}もしも運命があるのならば　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.15,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}「あなたは運命の人」なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:31.99,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}そんな言葉今を壊しそうで言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:34.61,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}近くに居ても遠く感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:37.13,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}行ったり来たりしてるこの想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:40.14,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}諦める　諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:42.29,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}終わらない花占い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:44.73,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}宝箱の鍵失ったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:47.35,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}キラキラした想いて抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:54.89,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}仄かに色付いた欠片をため息に隠す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:05.35,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}目が合ったなら逸らさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.93,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}秘められたこの嘘を見抜いてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:10.41,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}限界がもう分からないの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:13.20,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}だから今は何も言わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:20.26,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}苦しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:24.19,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}怖いほどあなたが好き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:14.50,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}最寶貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:16.97,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}最想要去珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:21.56,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}如此簡單的事情現在卻最無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:24.43,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}若是真的存在命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.15,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}「你就是我的命定之人」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:31.99,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}無法說出口 懼怕這些話語將會毀掉現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:34.61,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}近在咫尺卻彷若遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:37.13,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}反覆無常的這份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:40.14,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}放棄 還是堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:42.29,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}永無止境的花瓣占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:44.73,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}若然丟失了寶箱的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:47.35,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}抱緊最後一絲希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:54.89,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}將逐漸泛紅的碎片藏進一聲聲嘆息中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:05.35,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}如果看著我 請不要移開目光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.93,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}讓你看透我所隱藏的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:10.41,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}我不知自己能堅持到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:13.20,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}所以現在請你沉默就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:20.26,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}愛的如此痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:24.19,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}愛的如此恐懼
